This code read the 2018 October TB rechit ntuple to produce Shower Shape variable

input data file path:
/eos/cms/store/group/dpg_hgcal/tb_hgcal/2018//eos/cms/store/group/dpg_hgcal/tb_hgcal/2018/cern_h2_october/prompt_reco
input MC file path:
Not ready yet

For the run information please refer to:
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1FlwthMixJHmHVBguYSbw5mIeBo2tF7rFJPTYLTNI9Vs/edit?usp=sharing

*************************************************************************
Downwards are outdated(currently just type ./makePlots to run the code)**
*************************************************************************

To Run:
(Data -> For example run 316)

make
ls /eos/cms/store/group/dpg_hgcal/tb_hgcal/2018/cern_h2_june/offline_analysis/ntuples/v9/ntuple_316.root > input.txt
./makePlots or ./makePlots 1

(MC)
make
ls /eos/cms/store/group/dpg_hgcal/tb_hgcal/2018/cern_h2_june/offline_analysis/sim_ntuples/v9/ntuple_sim_pdgID11_beamMomentum100.0_listFTFP_BERT_EMM.root > input.txt
./makePlots 0

The output file will be store in output_root
